### Task Manager REST API
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client
### Install: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ─── Health ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### ─── CREATE TASK ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a task (all fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Fix login bug",
  "description": "Users cannot log in with Google OAuth on mobile devices",
  "status": "todo",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2027-12-31",
  "tags": ["backend", "auth", "bug"]
}

###

### Create a minimal task (title only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Write unit tests"
}

###

### Create task — validation error (title too short)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "ab",
  "priority": "ultra"
}

###

### Create task — validation error (past dueDate)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Overdue task example",
  "dueDate": "2020-01-01"
}


### ─── LIST TASKS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all tasks (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks

###

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=todo

###

### Filter by priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?priority=high

###

### Filter by status AND priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=in-progress&priority=medium

###

### Filter by tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?tags=backend

###

### Filter by multiple tags (comma-separated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?tags=backend,auth

###

### Filter tasks due before a date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?dueBefore=2027-06-01

###

### Sort by dueDate ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=dueDate&order=asc

###

### Sort by createdAt descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=createdAt&order=desc

###

### Pagination — page 2, 5 items per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=2&limit=5

###

### Combined — filter + sort + pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=todo&priority=high&sortBy=dueDate&order=asc&page=1&limit=10


### ─── STATS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get aggregate stats
### NOTE: /stats must come before /:id in routes — this would fail if routes were reversed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/stats


### ─── GET SINGLE TASK ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get task by ID — replace with a real ID from a previous response
@taskId = REPLACE_WITH_REAL_TASK_ID

### Get task by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}

###

### Get task — invalid ObjectId format (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/not-a-valid-id

###

### Get task — valid ObjectId that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000


### ─── UPDATE TASK ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Update status only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "in-progress"
}

###

### Update multiple fields
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "priority": "medium",
  "tags": ["backend", "refactor"],
  "dueDate": "2027-11-30"
}

###

### Update — validation error (empty body, expect 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

###

### Update — invalid status value (expect 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}


### ─── DELETE TASK ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete task by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}

###

### Delete — invalid ObjectId (expect 400)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/not-a-valid-id

###

### Delete — already deleted / not found (expect 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000
